caption.p: Influences of SPP on regulation of apoptotic signal proteins in HL-60 ( A) and CCRF-SBA ( B) cells. All experiments were repeated at least three times, obtaining similar results. Both cells were treated with SPP (0–500 µg/mL) for 48 h. β-Actin was used as a control, (–), 0.1% DMSO-treated cells. The experiments were carried out in three replicates.
